</script></li></ul><div id='article-body'>
        <h2 property="dc:title">
    Obama&#039;s Crackdown on Whistleblowers    </h2>
        <div class="article-teaser"><p>The NSA Four reveal how a toxic mix of cronyism and fraud blinded the agency before 9/11.</p>
</div>
    
  <div class="views-field-value byline">
    <a href="/authors/tim-shorrock"><span property="dc:creator">Tim Shorrock</span></a>  </div><!--/views-field-value-->
  <div class="article-info-string">
    <span class="article-date">March 26, 2013</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;
          <span class="border">|</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;
      <span class="article-appeared">
        <a href="/issue/april-15-2013">This article appeared in the April 15, 2013 edition of The Nation.</a>      </span>
      </div><!--/article info string-->
